{\an8}Now let us download
the holy tweet of the Lord.

15
00:00:46,546 --> 00:00:48,626
{\an8}Stop making this relatable.

16
00:00:48,715 --> 00:00:50,335
{\an8}Hey, as a youth,

17
00:00:50,425 --> 00:00:53,045
{\an8}if I don't hear a computer word
every couple sentences,

18
00:00:53,136 --> 00:00:54,386
{\an8}I am outta here.

19
00:00:54,471 --> 00:00:55,851
{\an8}Duly noted.

20
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:58,850
{\an8}But we will make sure
not to dilute the sacred gospel.

21
00:00:58,933 --> 00:01:01,143
{\an8}Mouse pad!
Double click! Skype!

22
