{\an8}"Then spake Jesus
to the multitude,

26
00:01:08,693 --> 00:01:10,903
{\an8}and to his disciples, saying..."

27
00:01:10,987 --> 00:01:13,407
{\an8}HOMER:
Hey, my bathing suit came off!

28
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,660
{\an8}Whoo!

29
