00:11:14,382 --> 00:11:15,722
Or even a Milhouse.

265
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,300
I don't know what <i>is</i>
"Milhouse."

266
00:11:17,385 --> 00:11:18,585
(grunting)

267
00:11:18,678 --> 00:11:20,598
I work security
for the tour.

268
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:22,560
Dealing with American
punks like you

269
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,020
