military service.

270
00:11:24,100 --> 00:11:26,140
And we know
<i>all </i>about you.

271
00:11:27,228 --> 00:11:29,058
BART:  <i>Ay, caramba.</i>

272
00:11:29,146 --> 00:11:32,106
Hey, is that
the Ark of the Covenant?

273
00:11:32,191 --> 00:11:33,111
(grunting)

274
00:11:33,192 --> 00:11:34,942
Karate!

275
00:11:35,027 --> 00:11:37,607
Once again, Krav maga!

276
00:11:37,697 --> 00:11:39,697
(grunting)

277
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:41,242
Quit going for my groin!

278
00:11:41,325 --> 00:11:43,035
No groin, no Krav maga.

279
00:11:43,119 --> 00:11:44,369
(grunting in pain)

280
00:11:44,453 --> 00:11:46,083
Hello, groin.

