in one small room, and...

307
00:12:46,474 --> 00:12:48,144
it's so nice and cool

308
00:12:48,225 --> 00:12:50,935
-in the Tomb
of the Unknown Savior.
-Unknown?

309
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:53,690
This is the tomb of the most
famous man who ever lived!

310
00:12:53,773 --> 00:12:54,823
Porky Pig?

311
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:56,189
Porky Pig's not a man!

312
00:12:56,275 --> 00:12:59,485
He's a pig, and he's
not even a real pig!

313
00:12:59,570 --> 00:13:02,410
But he <i>is</i>
buried here, right?

314
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:04,620
That's it!
