in your camera are
of funny soda pops?

318
00:13:12,082 --> 00:13:13,212
(groans)

319
00:13:13,292 --> 00:13:14,132
Oh, will you...

320
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:15,340
You are such a...

321
00:13:15,419 --> 00:13:16,629
Ah!

322
00:13:16,712 --> 00:13:19,172
