Chickpea Fizz!

323
00:13:19,256 --> 00:13:21,336
Delete. Delete. Delete.

324
00:13:21,425 --> 00:13:22,885
Whatever.
It's <i>your </i>camera.

325
00:13:22,968 --> 00:13:24,258
(screams)

326
00:13:24,345 --> 00:13:25,175
(grunts)

327
00:13:25,262 --> 00:13:27,262
(grunting,
thumping)

328
00:13:27,348 --> 00:13:29,388
(grunts)

329
00:13:31,143 --> 00:13:33,103
Please, you've got
to let me back in.

330
00:13:33,187 --> 00:13:35,437
I sold 6,000 rolls
of wrapping paper to get here.

331
00:13:35,523 --> 00:13:36,573
That's <i>your </i>problem.

332
00:13:36,649 --> 00:13:38,029
You, my friend, are banned

333
00:13:38,108 --> 00:13:39,648
from ever entering
this church again.

334
00:13:39,735 --> 00:13:40,565
(slams door)

335
00:13:40,653 --> 00:13:42,823
B-Banned for life?

336
00:13:42,905 --> 00:13:45,365
Homer, do you know
why I'm a Christian?

337
00:13:45,449 --> 00:13:46,779
Your parents made you?

338
00:13:46,867 --> 00:13:49,157
It's because I
believe every soul

339
00:13:49,245 --> 00:13:51,365
has the possibility
of salvation.

340
00:13:51,455 --> 00:13:53,955
At least I thought so
till now.

341
00:13:54,041 --> 00:13:57,921
Homer Simpson,
you are not worth saving.

342
00:13:58,003 --> 00:14:00,803
What? But I thought
we'd be neighbors in Heaven.

343
00:14:00,881 --> 00:14:03,551
-Goofing on all
the new dead people.
-Not...

344
00:14:03,634 --> 00:14:06,014
